{"segment":1,"line_start":1,"line_end":92,"dialogues":[{"speaker":"char_chang_ping_jun","speaker_name":"昌平君","listener":"char_xiang_shao_long","text":"赌你输的人，听得你昨晚大战'醉风四花'，现在仍能稳坐马上，必是大大失望。","tone":"调侃","chapter":204,"line_start":34,"line_end":36},{"speaker":"char_xiang_shao_long","speaker_name":"项少龙","listener":"char_chang_ping_jun","text":"今晚我若输了，恐怕以后休想踏进乌家之门，因为岳丈大人在我身上押下重注，假如累他输钱，你说会有什么后果？","tone":"调侃","chapter":204,"line_start":38,"line_end":40},{"speaker":"char_chang_ping_jun","speaker_name":"昌平君","listener":"char_xiang_shao_long","text":"原来贵丈人也爱豪赌。","tone":"惊讶","chapter":204,"line_start":42,"line_end":42},{"speaker":"char_xiang_shao_long","speaker_name":"项少龙","listener":"char_chang_ping_jun","text":"不是爱赌，而是爱看蒲鶮输得损手烂脚，看他还凭什么去笼络那些贪财的王亲国戚、公卿大臣。","tone":"低语","chapter":204,"line_start":44,"line_end":46},{"speaker":"char_tu_xian","speaker_name":"图先","listener":"char_xiang_shao_long","text":"那小子身内暗穿来自越国巧匠的软甲，最好攻他头脸，否则拼着捱你一枪，他就可置你于死地。","tone":"低语","chapter":204,"line_start":50,"line_end":52},{"speaker":"char_xiang_shao_long","speaker_name":"项少龙","listener":"char_tu_xian","text":"我今晚何来什么枪呢？","tone":"低语","chapter":204,"line_start":54,"line_end":54},{"speaker":"char_xiang_shao_long","speaker_name":"项少龙","listener":"char_lu_dan_er","text":"快嫁人哩！见到长辈，却不来恭敬行礼请安，成什么体统？","tone":"调侃","chapter":204,"line_start":70,"line_end":71},{"speaker":"char_lu_dan_er","speaker_name":"鹿丹儿","listener":"char_xiang_shao_long","text":"哼！你是谁的长辈，我嫁不嫁人关你什么事？","tone":"愤怒","chapter":204,"line_start":73,"line_end":74},{"speaker":"char_lu_dan_er","speaker_name":"鹿丹儿","listener":"char_xiang_shao_long","text":"你坏死了！竟欺负我。","tone":"愤怒","chapter":204,"line_start":78,"line_end":80},{"speaker":"char_xiang_shao_long","speaker_name":"项少龙","listener":"char_lu_dan_er","text":"好丹儿！我项少龙等着喝你那杯跪着奉上来的喜酒呢！","tone":"得意","chapter":204,"line_start":82,"line_end":84},{"speaker":"char_ying_ying","speaker_name":"嬴盈","listener":"char_xiang_shao_long","text":"项大人！","tone":"陈述","chapter":204,"line_start":88,"line_end":88},{"spea